<L>__{interior ambrose chapel (day) close shot}
<A>__{mr. drayton, trying to puzzle out her alarm, studies her face, and then lifts his eyes to look beyond her. the expression on his face leaves no doubt that he cannot understand what she's trying to convey. the hymn has come an end, and the congregation starts seating itself.}
<L>__{interior ambrose chapel (day) medium close shot}
<A>__{the mckennas take a seat along with the rest, and as yet they are relatively inconspicuous from the front of the chapel. ben takes a piece of paper out of his pocket, examines it, and satisfied it is the right one, hands it to his wife. the congregation falls silent as drayton is apparently about to begin his sermon.}
